{
  "stem": "19502.1",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 448.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it would change us to the good and to the bad.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see, like, for my mother was a blessing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You see, she had her family.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "On my father's side, it was a curse.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And for us children, we had a good time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We just didn't know any better.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We just were happy-go-lucky.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were singing war-- songs about the war, about Stalin, about [INAUDIBLE], and about, you know, that the-- the-- who had the first one, the Russian army will take everything away, and the [INTERPOSING VOICES] Communists will be against the best and so on and so forth.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I just thought that's the way-- they came in school.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They told me that the man comes from a-- a-- a-- a monkey not a damsel.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, I mean, they brainwashed us so much that religion was put aside.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But yet in the Constitution-- when we took in school the Constitution, the Russian Constitution-- they said, you can have your religion, but we don't support your churches.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You see, you have to support that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But it didn't mean a thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were too much brainwashed as children.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We've finished the first tape.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
